document_data.name: Westgate Market Street
document_data.mainbody: '''Westgate Market Street''' was a major avenue found in the city of [[Westgate]].
document_data.Location: Westgate Market Street entered the city through [[Mulsantir's Gate]]. It passed southeast through the center of the city before terminating with [[Woodside Way]] in front of [[Castle Thorsar]] in the south section of the city. Along the way Westgate Market Street intersected with [[Westlight Walk]], [[Wagonwheel Ride]], [[Sword Lane]], [[Brewhouse Lane]], [[Silverpiece Way]], [[Southgate Market Street]], and [[East Market Street]].
document_data.Inhabitants: Notable people who lived on Westgate Market Street included the [[wizard]] [[Gondeth]], High Priest [[Hunn Irblast]], and High Articifer [[Ashuntira Elhorn]].
